{
  "texts": [
    "We repeated this process 10 times in total, each time with a new GPT reappraisal per subset.",
    "We were left with 10 GPT percentile ranks per vignette.",
    "We took the average of all these percentile ranks to obtain the final average percentile rank of 85 th (Figure 2).",
    "Understanding Differences in Human Reappraisal Ratings.",
    "Given the observed reappraisal quality gap, we examined whether time spent on reappraisal predicted the quality of reappraisal."
  ]
}